# Agustin Suarez Merino - Personal Portfolio Website

## Overview
A modern, responsive personal portfolio website showcasing Agustin Suarez Merino's work as a Software Engineer & Entrepreneur. The site is built with Next.js 15, React 19, and TypeScript, featuring a clean, professional design with multi-language support (English and Spanish).

